metadata.name: Reverberations #127
metadata.description:
[ CLICK TO START THE SOUND ]
Best viewed on a decent GPU for 60fps rendering
Play the instrument by clicking or touching the blobs
Supports any aspect ratio, however the resulting simulation will vary!

Everything in the universe is made up of vibrating energy, including us. Our thoughts and emotions are also vibrations of energy that influence the frequencies around us. 
Be kind.

Controls
[ click / touch ] - split blobs
[ /?play ] - query string to avoid automatic splits
[ s ] - save image
[ f ] - full screen

Created with Three.js + Rapier.js + Tone.js

metadata.name: Murmuration #70
metadata.description: A "murmuration" describes both a swarm of starlings, as well as a low continuous sound. This piece reflects on both phenomena, and uses sound waves as the point of origin for the visual interpretation. The non-repetitive nature of the overlapping oscillations form the basis of a potentially endless experience. Four pre-synthesized waveforms spread across the soundstage have been arranged to highlight the emotional quality of the selected mode. Developed as part of the Forefront Web3 Creator Residency
